import React from'react'
import {BrowserRouter,Routes,Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import App from './App'

function AppRouter() {
    return(
        <BrowserRouter>
        <App></App>
        <Routes>
            <Route path='/' element={App}/>
            <Route path='/create'/>
        </Routes>
        </BrowserRouter>

    )
}
export default AppRouter
